org.hibernate.ogm.transaction.emulated.impl

Class EmulatedLocalTransactionCoordinatorBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.transaction.emulated.impl.EmulatedLocalTransactionCoordinatorBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, TransactionCoordinatorBuilder, Service

    public class EmulatedLocalTransactionCoordinatorBuilder
extends Object
implements TransactionCoordinatorBuilder
    Builds non-JTA-based TransactionCoordinators which use a no-op JdbcResourceTransaction and connection. That way flushes are triggered as expected - and written to the datastore, but no actual transaction is involved.
    Author:
    Gunnar Morling
